OL,3,CNew #22m diagnostic centre expected to
OL,4,C'revolutionise' healthcare
OL,6,FRachel O'Connor, director of
OL,7,Fintegrated care, told ITV News the new
OL,8,Fcentre would 'revolutionise' patient
OL,9,Fcare.
OL,11,FA new community diagnostic centre has
OL,12,Fopened in Plymouth, allowing people to
OL,13,Fundergo tests and scans closer to home.
OL,15,FThe #22million facility in Western
OL,16,FApproach will offer around 330
OL,17,Fappointments per day, helping to
OL,18,Freduce waiting times and improve
OL,19,Fpatients' experience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
