CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782141507
OL,3,CNew #22m diagnostic centre expected to
OL,4,C'revolutionise' healthcare
OL,6,FThe centre is equipped with state-of-
OL,7,Fthe-art diagnostic technology,
OL,8,Fincluding two MRI scanners, two CT
OL,9,Fscanners and two X-ray rooms.
OL,11,FAdditional services include
OL,12,Fultrasound, phlebotomy, lung function
OL,13,Ftesting and audiology.
OL,15,FJohn Stephens, director of estates and
OL,16,Ffacilities said: "This centre will
OL,17,Fmake a significant impact. Over 300
OL,18,Fpatients will pass through here every
OL,19,Fsingle day, seven days a week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
