OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782141507
OL,3,CNew #22m diagnostic centre expected to
OL,4,C'revolutionise' healthcare
OL,6,F"That represents a huge step forward
OL,7,Fin tackling the health inequalities we
OL,8,Fset out to address, and in supporting
OL,9,Fearlier detection of disease - which
OL,10,Fwe know is crucial to improving
OL,11,Foutcomes and saving lives."
OL,13,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,14,FSutton and Devonport, said: "These
OL,15,Ffacilities will deliver vital
OL,16,Fdiagnostic services such as MRIs, CT
OL,17,Fscans and X-rays, and by moving over
OL,18,F91,600 tests a year into the city
OL,19,Fcentre, we are making healthcare more
OL,20,Faccessible for residents, while taking
OL,21,Fpressure off Derriford Hospital."
OL,26,@vD@]OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
