CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782141507
OL,3,CNew #22m diagnostic centre expected to
OL,4,C'revolutionise' healthcare
OL,6,FDr Trevor Smith, NHS England South
OL,7,FWest regional medical director, said:
OL,8,F"This modern building in the heart of
OL,9,Fthe city will help many more people
OL,10,Fget tests and scans, more than 91,600
OL,11,Feach year and appointments every day
OL,12,Ffrom 8am to 8pm.
OL,14,F"By bringing these services closer to
OL,15,Fhome, people can be seen more quickly
OL,16,Fand easily, helping reduce waiting
OL,17,Ftimes and spot health problems earlier.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
