OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1782141507
OL,3,CNew #22m diagnostic centre expected to
OL,4,C'revolutionise' healthcare
OL,6,F"This centre is a great example of how
OL,7,Fpartnership working can improve health
OL,8,Foutcomes while contributing to the
OL,9,Fwider regeneration of the city, and I
OL,10,Flook forward to Plymouth CDC welcoming
OL,11,Fits first patient on 23 June, and
OL,12,Fhearing their thoughts on their visit."
OL,14,FThe first patients will arrive at the
OL,15,Fcentre from Tuesday 23 June.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]
